💙Le Grand Bleu 

One of the largest Expedition  yachts in the World. Once owned by Roman Abramovich.

Follows us @topyacht 

Her design features many ideas which make her ideal for exploration, including a large tender garage with storage for two sports boats as well as a landing craft capable of carrying a 4x4 Land Rover for excursions ashore.
